DRDGold Says Quarterly Gold Production to Fall About 3% to 67,400 Ounces

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-06T06:02:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/drdgold-says-quarterly-gold-production-to-fall-about-3-to-67-400-ounces.html
DRDGold Ltd. (DRD)  said group gold
production for the three months to March 31 is expected to fall
about 3 percent to 67,400 ounces from the previous quarter.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
